                     <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAM PIKE</hi> (22)</persName>
                  <rs id="t18600917-796-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18600917-796-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18600917-796-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, Stealing 110 pairs of uppers for boots, value 23<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. of <persName id="t18600917-name-326" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18600917-name-326" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18600917-name-326" type="surname" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
